result.title: Cool name for an acm team ?
result.content:
We have got the first place in our local Damascus DCPC ,our team name was O_0 :)

But now ,we've changed the team ,and trying to find a good name (who knows ,we may go to the ICPC this year ),I'm pretty sure that many others want to name there team with a special [cool] name;

for our team we have many possibilities like :

keep_coding=true;
KeepForward
2^43112609-1
keep::calm && code
Press any key to continue ...
^-^
koki_code

would you tell me the best,or provide others .

Thank you
